# Language Support Guidelines

## Overview
Giselle is a global project with contributors who include non-native English speakers. This guide outlines our approach to ensuring clear communication across language differences.

## Core Principles

- Please write in English
- Please correct grammar in commit messages, code comments, and pull request comments
- Rewrite user input when necessary to ensure clear communication
